-[THEME MUSIC PLAYS]

00:12.751 --> 00:16.799
-♪ SOME PEOPLE STAND
IN THE DARKNESS ♪

00:16.929 --> 00:20.846
♪ AFRAID TO STEP
INTO THE LIGHT ♪

00:20.977 --> 00:24.372
♪ SOME PEOPLE NEED
TO HELP SOMEBODY ♪

00:24.502 --> 00:28.115
♪ WHEN THE EDGE OF
SURRENDER'S IN SIGHT ♪

00:28.245 --> 00:30.639
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY

00:31.422 --> 00:33.816
♪ ITS GONNA BE ALL RIGHT

00:36.775 --> 00:38.603
♪ 'CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

00:38.734 --> 00:41.345
