♪ FOREVER AND ALWAYS

00:59.929 --> 01:01.931
♪ I'M ALWAYS HERE

01:20.906 --> 01:22.908
♪ 'CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

01:23.039 --> 01:25.389
♪ I WON'T LET YOU
